{
  "id": "68988eb05dff4e8210759b83",
  "title": "回転のスナップ",
  "created": 1754828476,
  "updated": 1754829066,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68988eb05dff4e8210759b83",
      "text": "回転のスナップ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828476,
      "updated": 1754828476
    },
    {
      "id": "68988f0300000000003f81e9",
      "text": " [VRChat]の快適性の設定の１つ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828548,
      "updated": 1754828679
    },
    {
      "id": "68988fa800000000003f81f0",
      "text": " \t既定で有効になっている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828713,
      "updated": 1754828719
    },
    {
      "id": "68988f6f00000000003f81ec",
      "text": " [VR]モード時の[VR酔い]対策のための設定",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828655,
      "updated": 1754828678
    },
    {
      "id": "68988f0f00000000003f81eb",
      "text": " 有効にすると、VRモードの時にスティックを倒してカメラを左右回転させた際に、8段階程度でカクカク回転するようになる。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828559,
      "updated": 1754828654
    },
    {
      "id": "68988f0300000000003f81ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828548,
      "updated": 1754828548
    },
    {
      "id": "68988faf00000000003f81f1",
      "text": "いいところ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828720,
      "updated": 1754828722
    },
    {
      "id": "68988fb100000000003f81f3",
      "text": "\tカメラの動きが抑えられるため、酔いづらくなる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828722,
      "updated": 1754828783
    },
    {
      "id": "68988fb000000000003f81f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828720,
      "updated": 1754828720
    },
    {
      "id": "68988fe300000000003f81f4",
      "text": "むずかしいところ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828772,
      "updated": 1754828774
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ff300000000003f81f6",
      "text": "\tカメラの微調整がしづらい",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828788,
      "updated": 1754828799
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ffe00000000003f81f7",
      "text": "\t\t自分の頭を[- 使って]動かして調整するしかない",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828799,
      "updated": 1754828815
    },
    {
      "id": "6898900500000000003f81f8",
      "text": "\t\t自分の直感に反したカメラ移動をするので、慣れていないと[空間把握]もしづらくなる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828806,
      "updated": 1754828965
    },
    {
      "id": "689890ad00000000003f81f9",
      "text": "\t\t[ゲーム系ワールド]のようによりリアルタイム性の高い操作が必要な際もやりづらいことがある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828973,
      "updated": 1754829008
    },
    {
      "id": "689890d000000000003f81fa",
      "text": "\t首が痛くなる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754829009,
      "updated": 1754829024
    },
    {
      "id": "689890df00000000003f81fb",
      "text": "\t\t微調整は頭を動かすしかないので",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754829024,
      "updated": 1754829030
    },
    {
      "id": "689890e600000000003f81fc",
      "text": "\t\t大抵のHMDは視野があまり広くなく目線を動かすということができない点も、より首への負担に拍車をかけている",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754829031,
      "updated": 1754829066
    },
    {
      "id": "68988fe300000000003f81f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828772,
      "updated": 1754828772
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ebb00000000003f81d9",
      "text": ">[https://x.com/vrcnavi/status/1833722980922441827 @vrcnavi]:",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828476,
      "updated": 1754828485
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ec500000000003f81e0",
      "text": ">[* VRChatをしてて酔うな...って方は]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828485,
      "updated": 1754828505
    },
    {
      "id": "68988eda00000000003f81e2",
      "text": ">",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828507,
      "updated": 1754828507
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ec100000000003f81da",
      "text": ">快適性とセーフティ👉回転スナップをONにしてみましょう。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828482,
      "updated": 1754828482
    },
    {
      "id": "68988edc00000000003f81e3",
      "text": ">",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828509,
      "updated": 1754828509
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ec100000000003f81db",
      "text": ">[* OFF]だと押してるとき一生ぐるぐる回るのですが",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828482,
      "updated": 1754828513
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ec100000000003f81dc",
      "text": ">[* ON]だと1回おしたらカクっと回って止まります。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828482,
      "updated": 1754828514
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ee400000000003f81e4",
      "text": ">",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828516,
      "updated": 1754828516
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ec100000000003f81dd",
      "text": ">実際私は酔いがこれでかなり緩和されました。OFFの方は是非1度ON試してみて下さい。",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828482,
      "updated": 1754828482
    },
    {
      "id": "68988eed00000000003f81e5",
      "text": ">",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828525,
      "updated": 1754828527
    },
    {
      "id": "68988eed00000000003f81e6",
      "text": ">他にもオススメの設定は下記のブログに纏めてます!!",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828525,
      "updated": 1754828529
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ef100000000003f81e7",
      "text": ">",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828529,
      "updated": 1754828530
    },
    {
      "id": "68988ef800000000003f81e8",
      "text": ">https://vrnavi.jp/vrchat-settexinngu/",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1754828536,
      "updated": 1754828537
    },
